## Context

- Forty-eighth run — Covered 11 projects with 11 new journal entries and 3 new tasks.
- Journal #2260 (wrn-msi-pancancer-atlas):
  - **VVD-214 JMedChem publication (2026).** Covalent allosteric mechanism detailed. Bayer/Vividion secured global rights from Roche (Jun 2025). Phase 1 mono+pembro enrolling, AACR 2026 early efficacy signals. NDI-219216 (Nimbus) completed dose escalation Part A (Dec 2025) — no DLTs, >24h target engagement, active against C727 covalent resistance mutation. IDE275 AACR 2026 abstract ND10. 6 WRN programs with clinical data, 3 distinct binding mechanisms.
- Journal #2261 (pancancer-mtap-prmt5-atlas):
  - **IDE892 FPI March 9 2026.** 1400-fold MTA-cooperative selectivity. NSCLC+PDAC enrolling. IDE892+IDE397 combo FPI mid-2026. AACR poster #4505. BMS-986504: 23% ORR (133 pts), 30% NSCLC, 31% go-forward doses, DOR 10.5mo. Phase 2/3 with Keytruda+chemo in 1L NSCLC — first pivotal PRMT5i. Bristol leads Amgen (AMG 193 12% ORR, combo discontinued). IDEAYA CDKN2A dev candidate H2 2026. Breast cancer PRMT5i gap persists.
- Journal #2262 (swisnf-metabolic-convergence):
  - **mSWI/SNF+KRAS combo preprint (bioRxiv Feb 27 2026).** FHD-286 sensitizes non-G12C KRAS-mutant NSCLC to pan-RAS and G12D inhibitors via EMT dampening. In vivo efficacy in KRASi-resistant models. Foghorn 2026: FHD-909 Phase 1 on track, CBPd-171 IND-enabling, ARID1B in vivo PoC, cash to H1 2028.
- Journal #2263 (rb1-loss-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
  - **INX-315 FDA Fast Track Feb 2026** for CCNE1-amp platinum-resistant ovarian. Phase 1: 10% PR, 63% SD (31 pts). Part C (CDK2+abemaciclib+fulvestrant breast) in progress. AACR 2026 P4-10-16.
- Journal #2264 (pten-loss-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
  - **AZD8186 development DISCONTINUED.** Limited clinical activity. GT220 (Geode/Dana-Farber) novel AI-designed PI3Kb inhibitor, 2x tumor:plasma ratio vs AZD8186, preclinical. GSK2636771 now only remaining clinical PI3Kb-selective program.
- Journal #2265 (crc-kras-dependencies):
  - **Zoldonrasib BTD for KRAS G12D NSCLC.** CRC expansion enrolling, no CRC data yet. ERAS-0015 AURORAS-1 advancing, mono data H2 2026. Cetuximab+MRTX1133 combo improving CRC responses.
- Journal #2266 (tp53-hotspot-allele-dependencies):
  - **Rezatapopt Orphan Drug Designation (March 2 2026)** for TP53 Y220C ovarian. PYNNACLE Phase 2: 33% ORR (97 pts), 43% ovarian. NDA Q1 2027.
- Journal #2267 (arid1a-pancancer-sl-atlas):
  - **Tulmimetostat Phase 2 ARID1A data.** Responses at 200mg (OCCC) and 350mg (EC). FDA FTD for ARID1A+ endometrial. Foghorn ARID1B degrader in vivo PoC 2026.
- Journal #2268 (keap1-nrf2-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
  - **DRP-104 Phase 2 enrolling** KEAP1/NFE2L2-mutant NSCLC. Glutamine antagonist synergizes with checkpoint blockade.
- Journal #2269 (nf1-loss-pancancer-dependency-atlas):
